enhancedSuggestions.title: Add 7 Missing Keywords
enhancedSuggestions.description: Your resume is missing 7 important keywords for Product Manager roles. ATS systems will flag this.
enhancedSuggestions.template:
Keywords to Add

Critical: These keywords are essential for passing ATS screening for Product Manager positions.

Add these keywords by category:

  • Tools & Technologies: product vision, revenue growth, strategic partnerships, digital transformation, innovation, business impact
  • Soft Skills: cross-functional leadership

Where to Add Them:

  1. Skills Section: Create or update a "Technical Skills" or "Core Competencies" section
    Technical Skills
    • Programming Languages: Python (Expert), JavaScript (Proficient), Java (Familiar)
    • Frameworks: React, Django, Flask, Node.js
    • Cloud & DevOps: AWS (EC2, S3, Lambda), Docker, Kubernetes
  2. Experience Descriptions: Weave keywords naturally into your bullet points
    Bad: "Worked on web applications"
    Good: "Developed scalable web applications using React and Node.js, deployed on AWS"
  3. Project Sections: Mention technologies in project descriptions

Important: Only add skills you actually have experience with. Be prepared to discuss any keyword on your resume in interviews.

Consider Adding Proficiency Levels:

  • • Expert: 3+ years, can mentor others
  • • Proficient: 1-3 years, comfortable working independently
  • • Familiar: Some experience, can work with guidance

quickFix.after: Added 7 keywords: product vision, cross-functional leadership, revenue growth, strategic partnerships, digital transformation, innovation, business impact...
